g\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f945dbfcb1e561eca346908edca5094eb0e6bef3","tid":1767530,"uid":85822,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:50:20.000Z","msg":"識玩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借個位宣傳吸引火力黎推post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nfor 想體力升級/心態提升為民請命手足參考<br />\n補師我要幫全世界身心升level<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入黎補補正能量整理下個人狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個人夠正能量先頂到落去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各做所長<br />\n若要勝利 必須備戰<br />\n營養＋運動 身心感覺同樣重要<br />\n<br />\n極權將破 在支爆前會係最黑暗嘅時候<br />\n幾艱難 損失都要打落去<br />\n<br />\n和理勇武強身強心飲食入門：<br />\n全世界維持健康打落去<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人人都要有自衞隊身體質素<br />\n香港人 團結反抗 無退路<br />\n未來嘅希望由我地做起<br />\n<br />\nStep 8.心理健康 正能量撚❤️<br />\n當我地遇到情況📍 在安全情況下<br />\n⚡️減少重複接觸影響自己的負面人事<br />\n🍎做自己鍾意的事<br />\n😀約定 定期運動放鬆 <br />\n🧠睇書/聽Motivation Video<br />\n🔥最緊要痴住正能量嘅朋友/人<br />\n<br />\n利申：健康教練<br />\nHerbalife  健康教練<br />\n唔係重點 重點係大家要長命幫手贏<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民皆兵</span></span> <br />\n依家風頭火勢 好多五毛<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 團結 正能量<br />\n呢個世界唔係我地影響人<br />\n就係人地影響緊我地<br />\n我地要內在夠強 百毒不侵<br />\n<br />\n永續健康身心 長期抗爭致勝<br />\n有咩搵我幫手 免費教大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港需要你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有需TG 唔問名 <br />\n幫你Case Study <br />\n教你點飲食點運動打仗飲食法<br />\n20％運動 80％營養<br />\n學完再善用Budget 搞好自己體能<br />\n得閒係屋企/搵我做下運動放鬆<br />\n行一陣街吸哂TG 暈低仲點打落去<br />\n<br />\nMy TG<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TreeHoIsGood\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTreeHoIsGood&d=QAb612WS2prazXX2mE0KsZbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=3480c6b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TreeHoIsGood</a><br />\nChannel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/treehoHealthAdvice\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FtreehoHealthAdvice&d=QAb612WS2prazXX2mE0KsZbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=e235b4be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/treehoHealthAdvice</a><br />\n討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/THHATalk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTHHATalk&d=QAb612WS2prazXX2mE0KsZbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=f5b71dc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/THHATalk</a><br />\n長期戰爭 齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對抗白色恐怖 <br />\n反共抗中 我地勢不兩立<br />\nWe Shall Never Surrender<br />\n<br />\nUnited, We can win the fight"},{"pid":"6ecede536c92f49815a931b3c50a909e7bc2772a","tid":1767530,"uid":149844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:50:47.000Z","msg":"幾時1兌1<br />\n港豬又要翻大陸做富豪了"},{"pid":"7e3f9f0f54e2b6c474602c9a6505e1eafe764485","tid":1767530,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:54:37.000Z","msg":"有冇人知侵侵連任到機率有幾高？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b2fa2b460e8750e88ddbf53f9fa7f1fa6f91481","tid":1767530,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:55:00.000Z","msg":"真。支爆"},{"pid":"e95bd3b3c79e725accec0100b11dccf76b52ff9c","tid":1767530,"uid":213812,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:55:08.000Z","msg":"Trump 仲有1年,又做多4年,然後到Pence做8年．甴主席無運行 !!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25af9cae5d5649a09211d2269dab3e533f95abf7","tid":1767530,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdcf0b1754bef6ceedbb4554325cb35d6ee8e56b","tid":1767530,"uid":133383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0